c], [http://www.drlue.tk/ical/?page_id=124 iCal Import/Export CalDAV]\n\n==Server implementations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 85%; text-align: center; width: 100%;\"\n|-\n! Server name\n! [[Software license|License]]\n! [[Programming language]]\n! RFC 2616 HTTP/1.1\n! RFC 2617 HTTP {{abbr|auth.|authentication}}\n! RFC 2518 Web&shy;DAV\n! RFC 3253 Web&shy;DAV {{abbr|vers.|versioning}}\n! RFC 3744 Web&shy;DAV ACL\n! RFC 4324 iCal {{abbr|CAP|Calendar Access Protocol}}\n! RFC 4331 Web&shy;DAV quota\n! RFC 4709 Web&shy;DAV mount\n! RFC 4791 Cal&shy;DAV\n! RFC 4918 Web&shy;DAV {{abbr|ext.|extensions}}\n! RFC 5397 Web&shy;DAV current principal\n! RFC 5545 {{abbr|rev.|revised}} iCal\n(Availability Check)\n! RFC 5546 iCal {{abbr|iTIP|transport-independent interoperability protocol}}(Group Scheduling)\n! RFC 5689 Web&shy;DAV {{abbr|ext.|extended}} MKCOL\n! RFC 5995 Web&shy;DAV POST add member\n! RFC 6352 Card&shy;DAV vCard\n! RFC 6578 Web&shy;DAV {{abbr|sync|synchronise}}\n! RFC 6638 Cal&shy;DAV {{abbr|sched.|scheduling}}(Auto-Schedule)\n! RFC 7529 iCal <!-- abbreviation? -->{{abbr|RSCALE|non-Gregorian calendar}}\n! RFC 7540 HTTP/2\n! RFC 7809 Cal&shy;DAV time zones by {{abbr|ref.|reference}}\n! RFC 7953 iCal <!-- abbreviation? -->{{abbr|VAVAIL&shy;ABILITY|personal availability}}\n! [http://www.calconnect.org/pubdocs/CD0903%20Freebusy%20Read%20URL.pdf <span title=\"FBURL\">Free-busy URL</span>]\n|-\n! {{rh}} | Ba\u00efkal<ref>{{cite web |url=http://baikal-server.com/ |title=CalDAV + CardDAV lightweight server: Ba\u00efkal |accessdate=2015-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114054905/http://baikal-server.com/ |archive-date=2015-11-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>[http://tech.tiq.cc/2013/10/how-to-set-up-the-baikal-carddav-and-caldav-server-with-nginx-on-debian/ Ba\u00efkal iCal export]</ref>\n| {{GPL-lic}}\n| [[PHP]]\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{Some}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{unk}}\n| {{no}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}